      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior has significant body damage, including major dents and areas of rust, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear. Mechanically, it requires substantial repairs to be roadworthy, as the engine runs roughly and there are noticeable fluid leaks. Please expect a vehicle that needs a lot of work and a full inspection before any attempt to drive it.",
